T02TD2404E:28b-1: a'a li k'a li mantra dzny'a na n'a ma /
T02TD2404E:28b-3: aa phreng ka phreng gi sngags kyi rim pa zhes bya ba /
T02TD2404E:28b-4: dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo /
T02TD2404E:28b-5: dbyangs dang gsal byed bzhi bcu rtsa dgu yi //
T02TD2404E:28b-6: bdag gzhan sgra yi rig pa'i sgra don ni //
T02TD2404E:28b-7: ba rdzi la sogs grangs kyang de don rtogs pa med //
T02TD2404E:28b-8: de byir gsal don bdag gis bshad par bya //
T02TD2404E:28b-9: sgra yi gnas ni brgyad yin te //
T02TD2404E:28b-10: rkan dang lce dang so rnams te //
T02TD2404E:28b-11: spyi bo mgrin pa mchu dang ni //
T02TD2404E:28b-12: khod pa sna la rnam par gnas //
T02TD2404E:28b-13: de yi dang po aa phreng ni //
T02TD2404E:28b-14: thun phyed bcu drug la sogs ldan //
T02TD2404E:28b-15: shes rab me long ye shes te //
T02TD2404E:28b-16: blo dang ldan pas shar par bya //
T02TD2404E:28b-17: de yi thob ma bcu bzhi pa //
T02TD2404E:28b-18: dbyangs can sgra gsal yi ge'o //
T02TD2404E:28b-19: de dag rnams kyi dang po ni //
T02TD2404E:28b-20: bcu ni mnyam pa'i ye shes so //
T02TD2404E:28b-21: skabs 'byung lnga ni thung ba ste //
T02TD2404E:28b-22: gzhan rnams ring bar shes bar bya //
T02TD2404E:28b-23: dbyangs rnams kyi ni thog ma gnyis //
T02TD2404E:28b-24: spangs te bcu bzhi'i ming can no //
T02TD2404E:28b-25: ae aee ao aoo bzhi dag ni //
T02TD2404E:28b-26: don dam kun rdzob 'bral yig go //
T02TD2404E:28b-27: aa ni stong pa'i thig le'o //
T02TD2404E:28b-28: zla ba nyi ma gtum mo'o//
T02TD2404E:28b-29: thig le gnyis ldan aa yig ni //
T02TD2404E:28b-30: drag po'i sgra ni dbye bar byed //
T02TD2404E:28b-31: ri r'i li l'i 'byung ba bzhi //
T02TD2404E:28b-32: dbye bas sreg byed yi ge'o //
T02TD2404E:28b-33: thung ba'i mig 'dzums skad cig gcig / mig 'dzums ring ba skad cig gnyis //
T02TD2404E:28b-34: skad cig gsum pa 'bod yig yin //
T02TD2404E:28b-35: skad cig phyed pa gsal byed de /
T02TD2404E:28b-36: rnal 'byor g-yon gyi phyogs su ni //
T02TD2404E:28b-37: dbyangs can bcu drug shes rab bo //
T02TD2404E:28b-38: de rnams sgra gnas 'di yin te /
T02TD2404E:28b-39: aa ku ha yig thig le gnyis la lhung //
T02TD2404E:28b-40: aa ni khong gi yi ge'o //
T02TD2404E:28b-41: ai tsu ya sha rkan la gnas //
T02TD2404E:28b-43: ri tu ra sha spyi bor grags //
T02TD2404E:29a-2: lte bar gnas te gyen la rgyu //
T02TD2404E:29a-3: ae ae mgrin pa ao aoo mchu //
T02TD2404E:29a-4: de yi thog mar chos dbyings so //
T02TD2404E:29a-5: de ltar aa phreng bshad byas nas //
T02TD2404E:29a-6: aa ka tsar ta pa ye sha ste //
T02TD2404E:29a-7: rtsa ba'i sgras ni de rnams so //
T02TD2404E:29a-8: ka las brtsams te ha yi mthar //
T02TD2404E:29a-9: g-yas phyogs gsal byed shes par bya //
T02TD2404E:29a-10: ka phreng lnga tshan lnga po ste //
T02TD2404E:29a-11: bzhi yi sgra yi reg pa'o //
T02TD2404E:29a-12: sha sha sa ha bcas pa ni //
T02TD2404E:29a-13: thog mar gnyis gnyis grangs min no //
T02TD2404E:29a-14: lhag ma gsum gsum sgra yin te //
T02TD2404E:29a-15: lnga tshan lnga ni sna las 'byung //
T02TD2404E:29a-16: mtha' la gnas pa'i 'byung ba bzhi //
T02TD2404E:29a-18: mtshan lnga yi nam mkha' la //
T02TD2404E:29a-19: sha sha sa ha drod can gnas //
T02TD2404E:29a-20: ksha ni k'a li ma mo 'dus //
T02TD2404E:29a-22: bskyed pa'i rim pa'i dbye ba yis //
T02TD2404E:29a-23: rgyu yi yi ge bshad par bya //
T02TD2404E:29a-24: ka nas brtsams nas ha yi bar //
T02TD2404E:29a-25: stir ro yi gdan yin no //
T02TD2404E:29a-26: ya ra la ba ma yis brgyan //
T02TD2404E:29a-27: mkha' 'gro rnams kyi bskyed thabs so //
T02TD2404E:29a-28: kam ni thod pa kha tv'am ga //
T02TD2404E:29a-29: tsha ni keng rus gdugs yin te //
T02TD2404E:29a-30: nga tshan lnga ni nyi ma yin //
T02TD2404E:29a-31: sha sha dur khrod shes par bya //
T02TD2404E:29a-32: sa bon yi ge bshad byas nas //
T02TD2404E:29a-33: k'a li rnal 'byor ngo sprod bstan //
T02TD2404E:29a-34: ka tshan ya dang bcas pa ni //
T02TD2404E:29a-35: zla gam sngon po nang nub la //
T02TD2404E:29a-36: phu phu sa dang gzhan la chags //
T02TD2404E:29a-37: ji ltar ri mo bri dang mthong //
T02TD2404E:29a-38: shar gyi yi ge rlung yin no //
T02TD2404E:29a-39: tsa tshad ra dang sha dang bcas //
T02TD2404E:29a-40: gru gsum dmar dang nyi ma phyed //
T02TD2404E:29a-41: zhe sdang dus su sprul yang bri //
T02TD2404E:29a-42: lho phyogs drag po'i gnas yin no //
T02TD2404E:29a-43: ta tshan bha dang bcas pa ni //
T02TD2404E:29a-46: ka li dzan dang 'bug ka ni //
T02TD2404E:29a-47: gti mug bya yi ri mo can //
T02TD2404E:29a-48: nub kyi phyogs su mo gdon no //
T02TD2404E:29a-49: ta tshan ksha dang na bcas pa //
T02TD2404E:29a-50: gru bzhi ljang ser nam phyed ni //
T02TD2404E:29a-51: sa dang rlung gi khams yin no //
T02TD2404E:29a-52: phrag dog dmar po rgyas pa'i dus //
T02TD2404E:29a-53: rmi lam rta dang stag mthong ba //
T02TD2404E:29a-54: rgyal pos bdag gdon gyi ngo //
T02TD2404E:29a-55: byang gi phyogs su 'dzin par bya //
T02TD2404E:29a-56: ba tshan sngon po chu rlung ste //
T02TD2404E:29a-57: gru gsum zla gam dbyibs dang ldan //
T02TD2404E:29a-58: nang nub dus su khams lci ba //
T02TD2404E:29a-59: rig pas rnal 'byor brtag par bya //
T02TD2404E:29a-60: de bzhin 'byung chung nyi shu lnga'i //
T02TD2404E:29a-61: gdams pa zhal nas blang bar bya //
T02TD2404E:29b-0: dri med shes @29b rab brgyan pa yi //
T02TD2404E:29b-1: thabs dang ldan pa'i sbyor ba ni //
T02TD2404E:29b-2: tha snyad mun pa rab bsal ba'i //
T02TD2404E:29b-3: de dag sems nyid stong pa bdag / tha snyad la bkod dge ba des //
T02TD2404E:29b-4: 'gro drug sdug bsngal zad phyir bsngo //
T02TD2404E:29b-5: a'a li k'a li'i rnal 'byor zhes bya ba slob dpon gandha sa mdzad pa rdzogs so /
